      • generate

        public static ShellProcess generate(java.lang.String[] aCommands,
                    java.lang.Integer[] aResultCodes)
        Auto generate command entries per each binary defined in com.spazedog.rootfw.container.ShellProcess.BINARIES.

        {"%binary df -h"} => {"busybox df -h", "toolbox df -h", "df -h"}

        Parameters:
        aCommands - Command to generate entries for
        aResultCodes - Result codes which defines successful execution (Defaults to 0)
        Returns:
        A ShellProcess container with all generated entries
